17
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:38,720
Don't hide in there and not speak!

18
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,000
Song Ziqi

19
00:01:42,190 --> 00:01:43,110
Open the door.

20
00:01:46,110 --> 00:01:47,360
Shut up.

21
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:48,720
Song Ziqi

22
