Song Ziqi. Get the heck out.

23
00:01:52,110 --> 00:01:53,550
I know you are here.

24
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:55,240
Come out now.

25
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,270
You are being suspended, so what?

26
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:06,000
Do you have to hide here and get so sullen about it?

27
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,520
Get out of the bathroom!

28
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:26,320
Hello.

29
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:28,670
You douchebag! You...

30
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:32,030
There's no need to...

31
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:32,910
Don't stop me.

32
00:02:32,910 --> 00:02:34,670
Shadi, calm down first.

33
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,670
You two get out.

34
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,470
I want to talk to him alone.

35
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,550
No...

36
00:02:39,670 --> 00:02:40,360
No, you...

37
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:56,440
How about

38
00:02:57,670 --> 00:02:59,160
I take you back to school?

39
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:09,440
My bag is still in there.

40
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,240
I'd better wait outside.

41
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,160
Can't you go easy on me?

42
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:25,270
If you hurt me, I won't be able to become a pilot.

43
00:03:26,670 --> 00:03:28,240
You still want to be a pilot?

44
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,550
Aren't you trying to stay away from everyone?

45
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,829
Aren't you running away?

46
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:33,630
You didn't pick up your phone.

47
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:35,800
Your QQ is off-line.

48
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:38,000
And you just sent me a message,

49
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:39,600
telling me that I should never try to find you.

50
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,360
Song Ziqi, who do you think you are?

51
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,240
Why did you treat me like that?

52
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:44,030
I am sorry.

53
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,390
Sorry?

54
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,550
You are just being suspended.

55
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,829
Big deal?

56
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,670
Do you need to avoid me like the plague?

57
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,160
Calm down.

58
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,510
I can't calm down.

59
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:57,550
Can't you just man up?

60
00:03:59,550 --> 00:04:01,440
You said you wanted to be with me.

61
00:04:03,550 --> 00:04:05,720
You said you wanted to be a pilot.

62
