63
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:11,830
And now, something went wrong.

64
00:04:12,230 --> 00:04:14,270
All you want to do is to hide. Not dare to confront it.

65
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:16,070
Song Ziqi, are you still a man?

66
